What is Floof - My Pet House Mod game? 


Floof - My Pet House Mod is an extremely entertaining pet care game in the educational genre. This game is designed as well as tested with children to help children learn faster and increase their ability to think creatively with a variety of models that simulate cute pets. This will stimulate the interest and curiosity of children. The publisher always tries to give players the most interesting, unique and meaningful experience.


When starting to participate in the game, players will adopt a lot of extremely cute and cute young dogs and cats. The task of those players is to raise pets by playing with them and feeding them every day. When the pets are hungry or thirsty, logos will be displayed on their heads. And the players will take pets to food so that they can be fed.


You will have to participate in an extremely fun puzzle game and win to be able to collect a lot of fruit and ice cream. The collected items will provide the pet. In addition, players will participate in skateboarding games to be able to pick up food for their pets. You can also cook delicious dishes for cute dogs and kittens to receive more coins from the contest. Let's experience the loveliness from the pets of this game together.


