Floof - My Pet House – Welcome to Your Virtual Animal Family!


Welcome to Floof -e for your pet dog, cat, and rabbit. Watch your pets’ growth by fostering a virtual animal family in the game. Play entertaining culinary, animal dress-up, puzzle, and adventure games while decorating their home. Your jobs include feeding, toilet training, washing, dressing up in adorable attire, and engaging in fun little activities with your animal family to take care of them.


An Adorable Animal Care Game


Don’t worry, younger children were considered while developing Floof – My Pet House. Similar to other pet simulation models, the game provides players with a fresh approach to learning while stimulating their imagination. The best part is that the creators are always working to deliver the most engaging and fulfilling experiences possible. Floof has a wide selection of elegant clothing that players can use to dress up their cute little pets. Each pet will have its own line of clothing that it can be dressed into.


Players will also have access to various accessories like caps, jewelry, sunglasses, shoes, etc in Floof. With these accessories, players will be able to make their virtual animal pets even more vibrant. Players can play with their cats, dogs, and rabbits to keep their mood up. In addition, they can also provide them with food and tuck them to bed. Other than that, players must also bathe them and potty train each one if necessary.


Explore Floof’s Imagination-Enhancing Games


You start Floof game by adopting a lot of adorable little dogs and cats. You will need to take the pets to the food when the logo appears on their heads that indicates whether they are thirsty or hungry. You can also play fun puzzles to acquire ice cream and fruits for your adorable pets. Or, show off your skateboarding skills and join the competition to win delicious treats for your virtual animal family. You can test your cooking skills by preparing meals which will earn your additional funds. Make sure their food dish is constantly filled plus give them regular exercise as well.


Children can improve their sensory perception by playing Floof – My Pet House. No matter their age, playing this game is an excellent way to boost their awareness. When you get a notification from your pet’s pet alarm system, you need to feed and hydrate your pets. You also need to provide basic grooming and nourishment to your rabbit, cat, or dog.


